collection.name: Worldwide Webb Land
collection.description:
Worldwide Webb is an interoperable pixel art MMORPG metaverse game giving utility to popular NFT projects. The game uses NFTs for in-game [NFT Avatars](https://opensea.io/collection/cryptoweebs), pets, lands, [NFT Items](https://opensea.io/collection/worldwidewebbitems)
, and quests. Deployed with a build-first mentality by a group of crypto-native game developers, artists, coders, and marketers; rapidly pushing out new technologies and applications.
